node.text:
Unwrapping the all new Mercedes Maybach S560 fresh out the factory! 😍
Just compare the sound inside and outside the car, incredible!
So satisfying to watch and pull off all the protection cover - can’t get enough of that 🤤
TAG A FRIEND and Mercedes Lover who has to see this! 👇🏼
Wish you all a great weekend 🌤
_______________________________
Mercedes Maybach S560 by @mercedesbenzrheinruhr 
@maybachluxury

#MercedesBenz #Luxury #Interior

node.text:
As promised here we have the next unpacking of the GLC63 S! Just check how smooth and satisfying it is to watch 🤤
This one is the Coupé version with 510 hp & V8 Biturbo engine! The fastest production SUV on the Nürburgring which pushed to 100km/h in just 3.8 seconds 😳
TAG your friend who has to see this! Soundcheck and SUV Comparison coming soon - so stay tuned for that 👌🏼
Wish you all a great weekend ❤️
_____________________________
Mercedes AMG GLC63 S supported by @mercedesbenzrheinruhr
